@startuml
title Transaction Flow: Purchase -> Payment -> Confirm
actor Mobile
participant API
database DB
participant Storage
participant PG as "Payment Gateway"

Mobile -> API: POST /events/{event}/purchase
API -> DB: BEGIN; SELECT ticket_type FOR UPDATE
DB --> API: locked
API -> DB: update sold; insert order, order_item
DB --> API: COMMIT
API --> Mobile: 201 {order_id}

Mobile -> API: POST /orders/{order}/payment/qris
API -> API: generate QRIS data
API -> Storage: put private/payments/{order}.png
API --> Mobile: 200 {qr_url}

Mobile -> Storage: GET signed qr_url
Storage --> Mobile: image/png

Mobile -> PG: scan & pay
PG --> API: webhook payment success
API -> DB: BEGIN
API -> DB: if pending -> update status=paid, paid_at
API -> DB: create ticket records
API -> Storage: write ticket QR images
DB --> API: COMMIT
API --> Mobile: payment status=paid
@enduml